description: After an easy dinner recipe that's ready in a flash? Try this flavourful chicken wrap with a crunchy salad and feta filling, it's ready in 15 minutes.
name: Speedy Chicken Wraps Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 500 g Woolworths COOK lemon & pepper chicken breast steaks
340 g Woolworths buffalo style salad kit
100 g South Cape Danish style feta
